  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Consolidating good governance and decentralisation with local actors</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PolicyPosition papers forums and debate &#xF0B7;
 Media engagements
Civic education
Community forums on Article 55(3) and Act 936 . Organise Town hall meetings for citizens .Identifying marginal groups and empowering them to participate in elections
Accountability forums

Organise public forums for presentation of position papers &#xF0B7;
 Identify and establish community activists to continue discussions of issues &#xF0B7; 
Get citizens to participate in referendum and elections</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthened horizontal and vertical linkages to address systemic local governance, public participation and inclusion challenges;
Promoted Issue-based and DA elections, including the election of women, PWDs and youth;
Enhanced citizen participation in the processes around the creation of new regions, election of MMDCEs and creation of new districts.</narrative>
  </description>
